Package airtrafficcontrol.app.menuoptions

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddAListOfFlightsOption
    This class represents the option with the title Add flights from the ListOfFlights.txt file. of an Air Traffic Control app for console.
    ConsultFlightDetailsOption
    This class represents the option with the title Consult a flight's details. of an Air Traffic Control app.
    ExitOption
    This class represents the option with the title Exit app. of an Air Traffic Control app.
    HelpOption_for_EHLsATCAppForConsole
    This class represents the option with the title Help! of the EHL's AIR TRAFFIC CONTROL app for console.
    MonitorAirTrafficOption
    This class represents the option with the title Monitor Air Traffic. of an Air Traffic Control app.
    Option
    This abstract class and all its subclasses represent options from an options menu.
    RemoveAFlightOption
    This class represents the option with the title Remove a flight manually. of an Air Traffic Control app.
    RemoveEmptyAirshipsOption
    This class represents the option with the title Remove all zero-passenger-flights. of an Air Traffic Control app for console.
    ReportTransgressionsOption
    This class represents the option with the title Report altitude transgressions. of an Air Traffic Control app.
    UpdateDatabaseOption
    This class represents the option with the title Update the database's flights' coordinates. of an Air Traffic Control app for console.
